[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "お待たせしました！　進んでいいですよ～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00245",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "なんとか、ブラオールに入国できた……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00246",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "タイニー、手続きの後処理は私が受け持つから\nお前は彼女たちを案内した後に本部へ向かえ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00247",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ランターナ王国からの船が到着した旨の報告と、\nついでに「九偉人図」についても調べてやるように",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00248",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "了解です、ボス！　案内人さんを案内しちゃいます！\nさあさあ皆さん、私についてきてくださ～い！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00249",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "大陸からの船、か……歓迎してやりたいところだが、\n何か騒動の匂いがするな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00250",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00251",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "おい、どうした？\n何やら思い詰めているようだが……具合でも悪いのか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00252",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "っ！！\nな、なんでもないんですっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00253",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "……害意はなさそうだったが。\nアルビーナの知り合いか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00254",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "おおお……！\nこれが諸島同盟最大の街、ブラオール……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00255",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "綺麗な街並みですね……！　\nなんというか、洗練された美しさを感じます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00256",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "すごくない？　道端にゴミひとつないわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00257",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "それはですね、ゴミをそのへんに捨てたら\n罰金！　だからなんですよ～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00258",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "えっ、そうなの？　厳しいわね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00259",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はい。ブラオールは美化にも力を入れてますので～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00260",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ボスいわく、「諸島同盟の中心地が汚れていては、\n同盟全体の威信に関わる」とのことで",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00261",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "キッチリしてるなあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00262",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ですね～。私も生まれ故郷はごちゃごちゃした所\nだったので、最初は驚きました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00263",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "でも、今ではすっかり慣れました。\n街の人も優しいですし、住みやすくていい街ですよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00264",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そういえば……監察官ってどういう仕事？\nなんとなくは分かるんだけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00265",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "島の治安を取り締まってる組織ってカンジ？\n王国の騎士団みたいに",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00266",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はい、そうです。ただし、取り締まりの範囲は\nこの島だけじゃなくて、諸島同盟全体に及びます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00267",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "同盟全体っていうと、小さい島も入れれば\nランターナ大陸よりも広いわよね。人手は足りるの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00268",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ぶっちゃけると、足りてません！\nなのでほら！　掲示板をご覧ください！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00269",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "手配書、この顔にピンと来たら……\n賞金が出るんですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00270",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "はい。こうして民間の方のご協力を募ってるんです。\n有力な目撃情報でしたら、賞金も出ます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00271",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "中には賞金首を直接捕まえてきちゃう\n賞金稼ぎな冒険者さんもいるんですよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00272",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "へぇ……面白そうじゃない。\nヌルスラの鷹、だって。変な名前",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00273",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あはは。その人、かなり迷惑かけてるんで、\nもし見つけたら教えてくださいね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00274",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "では、私はこれで！\n本部で「九偉人図」の情報を掴めたらすぐ伝えます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00275",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うん、ありがとう！\nお仕事、頑張ってね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00276",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]